{
  "stem": "21582.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And they were hooligans who were attacking Jews in the park, my park, where I fed my swans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I also remember the tremendous fear and shock that, that followed me when I heard on the radio about stabbings in these parks of Jews, which also was  not uncommon.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "I don't know how often they happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They probably were quite sporadic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "But they left a tremendous imprint, tremendous scars, on me then and even now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "I also remember that when I was very young-- when I was in first grade-- and when I, I used to break up in hives regularly.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "My mother took me to doctors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And all I remember that they could suggest to remedy it was for my mother to sponge my body to relieve the itch and, and, and, and, and the irritation.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "What happened was that when I used to go to school, we used to have to cross a Christian section.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And I don't know how many times-- but certainly too many-- some of the children chased us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "I remember running in panic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And I remember the parents who sat there and laughed because they were amused at our fear and our panic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "That really added to my fear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "Because look, I couldn't even count on the judgment of the adults.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "I couldn't even count that they would protect me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "After that, my mother, we, we were-- walked to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "But nevertheless, the faces still seemed so mean and just staring at us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And they were right there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "In spite of all of that, I-- when I think of my childhood, everything seems to be just absolutely drenched in golden radiance.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "It's a very special time for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "It really was my core.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "This, this is where I learned safety.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
